84
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,519
Brother Wang.

85
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,079
I'm begging you.

86
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,319
I just miss my Boss.

87
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,560
Just one look.

88
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,240
One look and I'll leave, okay?

89
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,519
