90
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,079
Captain Wang.

91
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,519
I've always seen you as a big brother.

92
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,879
I didn't think you'd be this cold-hearted.

93
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:36,199
Jiang Han.

94
