First of all, remember you're a cop.

95
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,519
I don't need you to remind me.

96
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,720
It's precisely because I'm a cop

97
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:48,600
