106
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,720
You're right.

107
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,480
I need to pull myself together.

108
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,720
I will find whoever killed my Boss.

109
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,800
That's the spirit.

110
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,639
If your Boss were here,

111
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:25,160
