113
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,839
The frustration you're feeling,

114
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,800
I understand.

115
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,040
And I know

116
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,439
