132
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,040
But not now.

133
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,360
Boss...

134
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,759
It's time to go back to the beginning.

135
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,360
Shen Qing, Ma Zhijiang.

136
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,879
What's the connection between them?

137
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,960
That club and Ma Shijiang's disappearance,

138
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,679
