147
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:25,720
This guy...

148
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,559
At the station, he acted so pitiful and innocent.

149
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:33,600
He's a complete psychopath.

150
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,120
Sister Lin,

151
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,679
