163
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,360
Don't be fooled by appearances.

164
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,879
Keep a close eye on him.

165
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,159
Don't worry, Captain Wang.

166
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,320
How's it going, viewers?

167
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:21,360
Hello, everyone.

168
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:23,879
Hello, everyone!

169
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,000
Stop.

170
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,120
Rewind it.

171
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,440
Hello, everyone!

172
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,799
Did you hear that sound in the background?

173
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,399
Sounds like...

174
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,759
