175
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,559
That's an old fishing boat engine.

176
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,360
Listen closely.

177
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,039
There's a ship horn, too.

178
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,360
And now,

179
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,120
