180
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:11,759
It really does sound like it.

181
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,519
How can you tell?

182
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,120
My grandparents were fishermen.

183
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,840
They lived in a fishing village.

184
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:19,799
These sounds

185
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:21,240
