186
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:26,679
A major breakthrough!

187
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,360
What breakthrough?

188
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,960
Captain Wang, perfect timing.

189
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,919
Jiang Han just analyzed the video and said

190
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:34,399
Red Gloves is likely hiding in a fishing village.

191
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,000
A fishing village?

192
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:39,879
And a very old one at that.

193
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,360
These houses

194
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:43,960
are all abandoned.

195
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:50,240
There are 15 fishing villages around Fengdu.

196
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:52,279
Only six fit the criteria.

197
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,320
Daqi Village is in Mingjiang County.

198
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,799
Caowu Village and Qiwan Village are in Lianhai District.

199
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:00,559
Zhenbei Village is in Luoxing County.

200
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,159
Baisha Village is in Xitan County.

201
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:04,159
Shangluo Village is in Qingyuan County.

202
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,799
Now, the arrest plan.

203
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:11,639
Six fishing villages.

204
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:15,159
One officer leads three others per village.

205
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,279
Search covertly in plain clothes.

206
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,360
Focus on abandoned old houses,

207
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,039
factories, and warehouses.

208
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:23,360
Listen carefully.

209
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:25,039
Notify the village officials in advance.

210
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,360
Do not tip them off.

211
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,360
Report immediately if you find the target.

212
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:32,919
Wait for orders before making the arrest.

213
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,679
Understood?

214
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:34,559
Yes, sir.

215
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:40,799
Captain Wang.

216
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,360
We lost Xing Mingliang.

217
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,679
Where did you lose him?

218
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,559
He took back roads on his motorcycle.

219
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:47,759
Judging by his direction,

220
00:12:49,399 --> 00:12:51,679
he's heading to Lianhai District or Luoxing County.

221
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,320
Lianhai District,

222
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:58,320
Caowu Village and Qiwan Village.

223
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,360
Zhenbei Village in Luoxing County.

224
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:02,759
Lin Xue.

225
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,879
Head toward Lianhai District and search.

226
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,960
Jiang Han will lead a team to meet you.

227
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:08,879
Remember this.

228
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,480
Do not act on your own.

229
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,679
Ensure your own safety.

230
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:12,759
Understood, Captain Wang.

231
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,799
Captain Wang, I'm heading out with my team.

232
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,039
Go ahead. Stay safe out there.

233
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,720
Follow me.

234
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:41,919
Fang Ping.

235
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:44,960
Lead a team to search Zhenbei Village in Luoxing County.

236
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:45,759
Yes, sir.

237
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:46,759
Understood.

238
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,720
Excuse me, sir.

239
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,600
Have you seen a motorcycle like this come through?

240
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:02,720
Yes, yes, I have.

241
00:14:02,919 --> 00:14:04,600
It just drove in over there not long ago.

242
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,679
Are there any abandoned houses in this village?

243
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,639
Yes, there are.

244
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:10,120
Over twenty families in West Village have moved out.

245
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,200
The county already has plans drawn up.

246
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,399
They're set for redevelopment.

247
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:15,120
Thank you, sir.

248
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,480
We're detecting abnormal signal fluctuations.

249
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:23,759
Cross-reference the signal with base station data

250
00:14:23,759 --> 00:14:24,519
