251
00:14:24,919 --> 00:14:25,679
Pinpoint the exact location.

252
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:26,840
Got it.

253
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,799
Just relax a little.

254
00:14:30,799 --> 00:14:32,120
What are you so afraid of?

255
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,879
Let's warm up first, shall we?

256
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:36,879
You.

257
00:14:39,159 --> 00:14:39,799
You.

258
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:42,919
You're the one.

259
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,759
Come on.

260
00:14:47,679 --> 00:14:48,799
Hurry up, get over here.

261
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,080
Don't!

262
00:14:55,279 --> 00:14:56,039
Brother Mingliang.

263
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:58,840
Let me do it.

264
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:02,159
I'll do my best to play along with your show.

265
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,799
My princess.

266
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:08,799
You've finally come around.

267
00:15:09,399 --> 00:15:10,039
Come.

268
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:11,720
Let me help you down from the carriage.

269
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:20,159
Come.

270
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:23,000
Come on, my princess.

271
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,679
Come.

272
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:31,720
Come on.

273
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,120
Freshly boiled water!

274
00:16:07,799 --> 00:16:08,600
And now,

275
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,399
