276
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,120
Bare-Handed Treasure Grab!

277
00:16:17,879 --> 00:16:19,960
Come on, my princess.

278
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,279
Come on.

279
00:16:24,759 --> 00:16:25,440
Come on now.

280
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,559
I won't! I don't want to!

281
00:16:26,559 --> 00:16:28,080
Come on, it's easy.

282
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,440
Here are the rules.

283
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:32,879
I'll count to three,

284
00:16:33,279 --> 00:16:34,799
and you stick your hand in.

285
00:16:35,559 --> 00:16:37,960
Come on, the audience can't wait!

286
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:46,799
Come on.

287
00:16:46,799 --> 00:16:47,559
I don't want to!

288
00:16:47,679 --> 00:16:48,240
